            <br><br>
            <strong>Schools Of The Future</strong> -- Through a contract with the Hawai`i Community Foundation and in partnership with the Hawai`i Association of Independent Schools, HACBED provided facilitation and technical support for learning circles being formed in and between the 20 schools chosen to be part of HCF's Schools Of The Future
            <br><br>
            <strong>Youth Matters Network</strong> -- Through a contract with the Hawai`i Community Foundation, provided facilitation and technical support to establish and conduct learning circles for 18 nonprofit youth serving organizations in the YMN.
